pr_title: Generalize parser and add access to the inner functions
pr_body:
- generalized parser and make it more legible
- added access to the low-level API: `build_loss_function`, `generate_training_sets`, and `get_loss_function` in order to get users more info about inner representation and give the ability to create a custom loss function and training sets. But it is the first step to this way
- added Stochastic Loss Function
- removed NNODE and solver overload
- refactoringdiscretize and PhysicsInformedNN
- use GalacticOptim solver
